Table.ScriptName: WU - Fix Windows Update Scan Time - Direct
Table.ScriptNotes:
Updates to install to decrease Windows Update Agent scan time.
http://forums.wsusoffline.net/viewtopic.php?f=7&t=5366
-Mike McGhee

ScriptSteps.Param1: SELECT COUNT(scriptid) FROM scheduledscripts JOIN lt_scripts USING (scriptid) WHERE lt_scripts.scriptguid='cfe4aaf4-b624-11e5-8ef6-00155d009007' AND (NOW() < DATE_ADD(scheduledscripts.NextRun, INTERVAL 55 MINUTE)) AND computerid=@computerid@
